{
  "texts": [
    "Though we have managed to identify various explanation attributes in an XAI system, our study does not capture users' viewpoints based on various explanation formats.",
    "Thirdly, another limitation is investigating explainability for more sensitive and highstakes decision-making in social media platforms.",
    "Finally, the participants in this study are primarily young, between 18 and 40 years old, and mostly have a good literacy level.",
    "Therefore, the findings in our study may not be generalized for all types of social media users.",
    "Drawing upon the limitations, we can propose future research directions (summarized in Table 2)."
  ]
}